    <entry>
      <title>Hexo搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2025/08/18/Hexo/"/>
      <url>/2025/08/18/Hexo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>基于hexo框架和github搭建个人博客网站，</p><h1 id="Nodejs安装"><a href="#Nodejs安装" class="headerlink" title="Nodejs安装"></a>Nodejs安装</h1><ul><li>Nodejs是hexo的运行环境，必须安装。Nodejs的安装可以参考：https:</li></ul><h1 id="Git安装"><a href="#Git安装" class="headerlink" title="Git安装"></a>Git安装</h1><ul><li>虽然这里安装了git，但是有关指令的操作我还是选择使用管理员权限下的cmd，权限问题可能会导致各种资源安装出错。git的安装可以参考：https：</li></ul><h1 id="Hexo安装"><a href="#Hexo安装" class="headerlink" title="Hexo安装"></a>Hexo安装</h1><ul><li>以管理员身份打开cmd，输入指令进行安装，如果你是按照上面的方式配置的Nodejs环境，那么你的<code>hexo-cli</code>资源应该在<code>Nodejs/node_global/node_modules</code>里<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/001.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/002.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><h1 id="Github部署"><a href="#Github部署" class="headerlink" title="Github部署"></a>Github部署</h1><ul><li><p>创建github仓库，仓库名为<code>用户名.github.io</code>，仓库public公开</p></li><li><p>配置git参数</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name 用户名</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name 邮箱</span><br><span class="line">git config -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>连接github，一路回车生成ssh密钥</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -T rsa -C 邮箱</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>【C盘】-【用户】-【.ssh】下记事本打开<code>id_rsa.pub</code>，这就是密钥，复制备用</p></li><li><p>【github】-【头像】-【Settings】-【SSH and GPG keys】新建一个ssh，粘贴上面的密钥</p></li><li><p>测试环境部署，注意需要关闭steam++</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/003.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><h1 id="Hexo项目创建"><a href="#Hexo项目创建" class="headerlink" title="Hexo项目创建"></a>Hexo项目创建</h1><ul><li><p>以管理员身份打开cmd，cd到想要放置项目的位置，创建hexo项目，需要打开steam++</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init 项目名</span><br><span class="line">cd 项目名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装依赖</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/004.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><h1 id="Hexo配置"><a href="#Hexo配置" class="headerlink" title="Hexo配置"></a>Hexo配置</h1><ul><li><p>进行hexo的基础配置，在<code>_config.yml</code>中，根据实际情况进行参数修改</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 用户名</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">description: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: 用户名</span><br><span class="line">language: en</span><br><span class="line">timezone: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url: https://用户名.github.io</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">theme: landmark //默认landmark主题，后续修改为butterfly主题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在本地进行浏览</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/005.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/006.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><h1 id="butterfly主题配置"><a href="#butterfly主题配置" class="headerlink" title="butterfly主题配置"></a>butterfly主题配置</h1><ul><li><p>这里使用butterfly主题，仅进行基础配置，参考：<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">https://butterfly.js.org/</a></p></li><li><p>cd到hexo创建的项目名根目录，安装butterfly插件，这里使用git安装，较为稳定</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装渲染插件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/007.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>在hexo根目录下新建一个<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>，并把主题的<code>_config.yml</code>复制过去（注意是主题的，而不是原来hexo的）</li></ul><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/008.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li><p>hexo会自动合并<code>_config.yml</code>和<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>里的配置</p></li><li><p>修改<code>_config.yml</code>中的主题<code>theme</code></p></li><li><p>在本地进行浏览</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/009.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><div align="center"><img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250820/010.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><h1 id="上传Github"><a href="#上传Github" class="headerlink" title="上传Github"></a>上传Github</h1><ul><li><p>在根目录下安装<code>hexo-deployer-git</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改<code>_config.yml</code>文件中的<code>deploy</code>部分，注意主分支是main还是master</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">type: git</span><br><span class="line">repository: git@github.com:用户名/用户名.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>部署到github，上传时注意关闭steam++</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl; hexo g; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
