      <title>Nodejs下载和环境变量配置</title>
      <link href="/2025/08/08/Nodejs/"/>
      <url>/2025/08/08/Nodejs/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Nodejs下载"><a href="#Nodejs下载" class="headerlink" title="Nodejs下载"></a>Nodejs下载</h1><ul><li>Nodejs官网下载链接：<a href="https://nodejs.cn/download/">https://nodejs.cn/download/</a> 选择64位的.msi文件</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/014.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>点击next开始安装</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/011.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>点击“我接受”，点击next下一步</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/009.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>更改安装路径，点击next下一步</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/015.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>默认选项，点击next下一步</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/012.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>默认不勾选，点击next下一步</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/013.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>完成安装finish</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/010.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>以管理员身份打开cmd输入指令，显示node和npm版本，表示安装成功  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/002.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><h1 id="环境变量配置"><a href="#环境变量配置" class="headerlink" title="环境变量配置"></a>环境变量配置</h1><ul><li>接下来进行环境配置，找到Nodejs的安装目录，新建两个文件夹<code>node_global</code>和<code>node_cache</code></li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/001.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li><p>以管理员身份打开cmd，输入指令查看原来的路径</p>  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config get prefix</span><br><span class="line">npm config get cache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入指令修改路径为刚刚新建的两个文件夹</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config set prefix &quot;xxx\xxx\node_global&quot;</span><br><span class="line">npm config set cache &quot;xxx\xxx\node_cache&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/005.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>【此电脑】-单击右键-【属性】-【高级系统设置】-【环境变量】，在“系统变量”下点击新建，变量名为<code>NODE_PATH</code>，变量值为<code>xxx\xxx\node_global\node_modules</code>，这一步完成后会生成<code>node_modules</code>文件夹</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/003.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/004.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>修改“用户变量”中的Path，点击编辑，修改为<code>node_global</code>路径</li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/008.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>修改“系统变量”的Path中，点击编辑，新增一条<code>%NODE_PATH%</code></li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/006.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>以管理员身份打开cmd，输入指令测试全局模块安装是否成功，如果正确安装，说明配置成功<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install express -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/007.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div><ul><li>继续输入指令，验证路径是否修改<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config get prefix</span><br><span class="line">npm config get cache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div align="center">  <img src="https://github.com/EvilGas/PictureBed/blob/main/img/20250817/016.png?raw=true" alt="图片描述" style="max-width: 650px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px;" /></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
